data.description: ASSUMABLE 2.7% LOAN AVAILABLE! Fabulous 5 bed / 4 bath single level home built in 2019 on corner lot in the sought after Glenwilde of Maricopa. Pristine curb appeal w/ paver drive (w/ RV gate) & perfectly placed, low maintenance landscaping, as well as delightful covered front porch. Great floor plan w/ neutral tones throughout, as well as wood plank style tile in all common areas. Versatile dining room flows to open living room w/ full wall of windows/sliders to back patio. Striking kitchen w/ popular white cabinetry w/ crown molding, SS appliances (including gas grill w/ hood), granite counters, custom tile backsplash & large island w/ sink, upscale pendant lights & bar top seating for the whole family. Kitchen flows to casual dining area w/ additional exit to back patio making entertaining a breeze. Primary bedroom has private bathroom w/ extended glass/tile shower w/ dual showerheads, dual sinks, private toilet & huge walk-in closet w/ shelving. Open bonus room/den in front of home makes perfect home office, game/play room or additional family area. And don't miss the bedroom w/ private bathroom & kitchenette perfect for guests or next gen living! Backyard has massive covered patio w/ extended shade pergola, fire pit, artificial grass area (for the pups!), additional open cement patio area perfect for BBQ or open seating & large side yard w/ room for RV parking. Bring a little love to the backyard & make it your own. Located near community park & w/ easy access to the 347 & all Maricopa has to offer. Be sure the schedule your showing today!
